data.title: PARKO'S JOURNEY TO THE 2012 ASP WORLD CHAMPIONSHIP

A collection of clips that featuring online, including interviews from Billabong founder Gordon Merchant, and close friends and family, have been strung together for your viewing pleasure.

data.title: North Shore Surf Trip
data.description: The North Shore is a proving ground for every surfer and so many of our girls have been there countless times. This past December, Courtney Conlogue, Lindsay Perry, Ellie-Jean Coffey, Alessa Quizon, Frankie Harrer,& Justine Dupont gathered at the Billabong house for Pipe Masters. Theymade sure to sneak off for some fun: surfing their favorite waves, eating Boba in Chinatown and jumping off the rocks and Waimea Bay. Check out the video the learn more about our girls and their trip.
